<#assign pop=JspTaglibs["/WEB-INF/taglib/pop-taglib.tld"]>
<#assign s=JspTaglibs["/WEB-INF/taglib/struts-tags.tld"]>
<@s.include value="/includes/baseInclude.jsp" />

<style>
.fontClass{
color: red;
font-size: medium;
font-weight: bold;
}
</style>
<div id="dialog-form" class="container container_20">
<img  src="${path }/resource/images/taskListRoleAll.png">
<div class='clearLine'>&nbsp;</div>
<div class="grid_4 lable-right">
   			<label class="form-lb1 fontClass">按月统计：</label>
</div>
<div class="grid_18 lable-right">
   			<label class="form-lb1">选择任意月显示当月数据，若选择本月记录的数据则是本月1号到今天相隔4小时实时数据。</label>
</div>
<div class='clearLine'></div>
<div class="grid_4 lable-right">
   			<label class="form-lb1 fontClass">按周统计：</label>
</div>
<div class="grid_18 lable-right">
   			<label class="form-lb1">选择上周就是上周星期一到星期天的数据。选择本周就是本周星期一到今天相隔4小时的数据实时数据。</label>
</div>
<div class='clearLine'></div>
<div class="grid_4 lable-right">
   			<label class="form-lb1 fontClass">按年统计：</label>
</div>
<div class="grid_18 lable-right">
   			<label class="form-lb1">就是本年的全部数据都是相隔4小时的实时数据。</label>
</div>
<div class='clearLine'></div>
<div class="grid_4 lable-right">
   			<label class="form-lb1 fontClass">异常：</label>
</div>
<div class="grid_18 lable-right">
   			<label class="form-lb1">流动人口的异常情况报告跟发现治安隐患一但录入就统计到异常列表当中。针对4类特殊人群信息的时候，</label>
</div>
<div class='clearLine'></div>
<div class="grid_18 lable-right">
   			<label class="form-lb1">选择了有异常的就会在报表里记录一条有异常。</label>
</div>
<div class='clearLine'></div>
<div class="grid_4 lable-right">
   			<label class="form-lb1 fontClass">回复：</label>
</div>
<div class="grid_18 lable-right">
   			<label class="form-lb1">流动人口的异常情况报告跟发现治安隐患只要网格员发现并发送到部门的数据在签收以后都必须点击回复，同样4类特殊人群信息</label>
</div>
<div class='clearLine'></div>
<div class="grid_18 lable-right">
   			<label class="form-lb1">在网格员发现有异常并点击异常发送出来以后，职能部门签收以后也必须回复。可根据实际情况多次回复，并可点击这条信息查看回复内容。</label>
</div>
<div class='clearLine'></div>
</div>	